rget%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Discovery%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20antitrust%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20Trump%20demanded%20that%20Netflix%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20terminate%26quot%3B%20Rice%20from%20its%20board%20of%20directors%2C%20%26quot%3Bor%20pay%20the%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20amplifying%20a%20message%20from%20right-wing%20activist%20Laura%20Loomer.%20Loomer%20had%20urged%20action%20against%20Rice%2C%20criticizing%20her%20role%20at%20the%20company%20and%20pointing%20to%20recent%20remarks%20she%20made%20about%20Trump%20and%20corporate%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERice%2C%20who%20served%20in%20senior%20roles%20in%20the%20Obama%20and%20Biden%20administrations%2C%20recently%20warned%20companies%20against%20aligning%20themselves%20too%20closely%20with%20Trump.%20Speaking%20on%20Thursday%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BStay%20Tuned%20with%20Preet%20Bharara%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20she%20said%20corporations%20that%20%26quot%3Btake%20a%20knee%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20president%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20break%20the%20law%20should%20expect%20consequences%2C%20predicting%20an%20%26quot%3Baccountability%20agenda%26quot%3B%20if%20Democrats%20take%20back%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clash%20comes%20as%20the%20streaming%20giant%20pursues%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwbd-warns-of-employee-exodus-paramount-skydance-david-ellison-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh-stakes%20merger%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20require%20approval%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice's%20antitrust%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20in%20December%20said%20that%20Netflix%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20big%20market%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20its%20potential%20acquisition%20of%20Warner%20Bros.%20%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20a%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20February%2C%20he%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bshouldn't%20be%20involved%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20deal%20and%20would%20defer%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-ted-sarandos-trump-warner-bros-sale-paramount-david-ellison-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20investigate%20the%20proposed%20merger%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20during%20an%20appearance%20on%20Puck's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Town%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20Netflix's%20co-CEO%2C%20Ted%20Sarandos%2C%20said%20that%20Trump%20hadn't%20asked%20for%20political%20concessions%20during%20discussions%20of%20the%20possible%20deal%2C%20but%20was%20focused%20on%20bringing%20jobs%20back%20to%20Hollywood%20after%20years%20of%20lower%20production.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Netflix%20and%20Rice%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-says-netflix-fire-susan-rice-warner-bros-deal-negotiation-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771736994000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699a76fd156648bc16a8a90d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-says-netflix-fire-susan-rice-warner-bros-deal-negotiation-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20weighed%20in%20amid%20negotiations%20over%20the%20Warner%20Bros.%20deal%2C%20saying%20Netflix%20should%20fire%20Susan%20Rice%20from%20its%20board%20%26quot%3Bor%20pay%20the%20consequences.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-says-netflix-fire-susan-rice-warner-bros-deal-negotiation-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pernod%20Ricard%20sees%20strong%20growth%20m