20to%20go%20to%20trial.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20terms%20of%20the%20settlement%20were%20not%20disclosed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECenterview%20Partners%20and%20former%20junior%20banker%20Kathryn%20Shiber%20have%20reached%20a%20settlement%2C%20ending%20a%20closely%20watched%20lawsuit%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-work-culture-shiber-centerview-trial-lawsuit-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20work%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20set%20to%20go%20to%20trial%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20centered%20on%20allegations%20that%20the%20boutique%20investment%20bank%20violated%20disability%20discrimination%20laws%20when%20it%20fired%20Shiber%20in%202020%20after%20she%20said%20she%20needed%20eight%20to%20nine%20hours%20of%20sleep%20each%20night%20because%20of%20an%20underlying%20mood%20and%20anxiety%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECourt%20filings%20and%20depositions%20in%20the%20case%20offered%20a%20rare%20look%20into%20the%20grueling%20demands%20placed%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-financial-firms-survey-across-investment-banking-pe-hedge-funds-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst-year%20analysts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20testimony%20that%20they%20typically%20work%20between%2060%20and%20120%20hours%20a%20week%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20some%20projects%2C%20you%20are%20working%2024%20hours%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%20Emails%20between%20Shiber%20and%20her%20higher-ups%20highlighted%20the%20unpredictable%20nature%20of%20the%20job%2C%20with%20her%20associate%20saying%20in%20one%20exchange%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20will%20always%20be%20more%20for%20you%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECenterview%20has%20denied%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCenterview%20has%20said%20all%20along%20that%20Ms.%20Shiber's%20legal%20claims%20have%20no%20merit%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Centerview%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20ready%20to%20prove%20that%20in%20court%2C%20and%20are%20confident%20we%20would%20have%20prevailed%20at%20trial.%20But%20we%20are%20nonetheless%20happy%20to%20put%20this%20distraction%20behind%20us%20and%20focus%20on%20delivering%20for%20our%20clients.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20means%20a%20jury%20will%20not%20weigh%20in%20on%20questions%20about%20Wall%20Street's%20long%20hours%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjunior-banker-analyst-life-centerview-partners-lawsuit-kathryn-shiber-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworkplace%20accommodations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20top%20bankers%20won't%20have%20to%20take%20the%20witness%20stand.%20Tony%20Kim%2C%20the%20co-president%20of%20the%20investment%20bank%2C%20was%20among%20those%20expected%20to%20testify.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJunior%20bankers%2C%20more%20formally%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-wall-street-investment-banking-after-fainting-bad-work-culture-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%20banking%20analysts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20tend%20to%20be%20recent%20graduates%20starting%20at%20the%20bottom%20rung%20of%20Wall%20Street's%20high-stakes%20dealmaking%20operations.%20They%20are%20often%20charged%20with%20grunt%20work%2C%20such%20as%20reformatting%20pitch%20decks%20or%20gathering%20data%20for%20a%20more%20senior%20coworker.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShiber%20joined%20Centerview%20in%20July%202020%20and%20was%20assigned%20to%20an%20active%20deal%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3BProject%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%20After%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F11-junior-banker-quit-goldman-sachs-healthcare-team-burnout-bonuses-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eworking%20till%20about%202%20am%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20several%20days%20in%20a%20row%2C%20she%2