r-development-true-cost-environmental-impact-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20space.%20Musk%20has%20made%20it%20a%20priority.%20Altman%20thinks%20it's%20a%20fantasy%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20honestly%20think%20the%20idea%20with%20the%20current%20landscape%20of%20putting%20data%20centers%20in%20space%20is%20ridiculous%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said%20during%20a%20live%20interview%20with%20local%20media%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Friday%2C%20causing%20audience%20members%20to%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20said%20that%20orbital%20data%20centers%20could%20%26quot%3Bmake%20sense%20someday%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20factors%20like%20launch%20costs%20and%20the%20difficulty%20of%20repairing%20a%20computer%20chip%20in%20space%20remain%20overwhelming%20obstacles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20there%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20added.%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20come%20a%20time.%20Space%20is%20great%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20things.%20Orbital%20data%20centers%20are%20not%20something%20that's%20going%20to%20matter%20at%20scale%20this%20decade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20would%20almost%20certainly%20disagree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20Big%20Tech%20and%20AI%20companies%20are%20spending%20billions%20on%20data%20center%20construction%20on%20Earth%2C%20Musk's%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20stars%2C%20per%20usual.%20Orbital%20data%20centers%20are%20his%20latest%20ambition%2C%20as%20he%20mentioned%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-all-hands-agi-superintelligence-funding-success-optimus-space%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall-hands%20xAI%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20SpaceX%20said%20its%20goal%20is%20to%20launch%20a%20%26quot%3Bconstellation%20of%20a%20million%20satellites%20that%20operate%20as%20orbital%20data%20centers.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20has%20already%20begun%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin