2%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Residents%20protest%20data%20center%20in%20New%20Brunswick%2C%20New%20Jersey%20in%20February%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6999fd85efb52c8bd0de9e9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221369%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EResidents%20in%20New%20Brunswick%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20protest%20a%20potential%20data%20center%20on%20February%2018.%3Cp%3EThe%20Climate%20Revolution%20Action%20Network%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnother%20possible%20data%20center%20has%20been%20scrapped%20after%20community%20objections.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20one%20was%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20where%20locals%20and%20environmental%20activists%20protested%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EData%20centers%20have%20become%20a%20flash%20point%20nationwide%20as%20AI%20companies%20scramble%20to%20power%20their%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20a%20modern-day%20Paul%20Revere%2C%20Ben%20Dziobek's%20voice%20rang%20across%20the%20night%20as%20he%20ran%20toward%20a%20crowd%20waiting%20outside%20New%20Brunswick%20City%20Hall%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%3F%20Members%20of%20the%20city%20council%20struck%20down%20potential%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-development-true-cost-environmental-impact-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuild%20a%20data%20center%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20canceled%20it!%20They%20canceled%20it!%26quot%3B%20Dziobek%20shouts%20in%20footage%20shared%20by%20New%20Jersey's%20Climate%20Revolution%20Action%20Network.%20Loud%20cheers%20followed%2C%20and%20then%20a%20chant%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%2C%20united%2C%20will%20never%20be%20defeated!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20Brunswick%20City%20Council%20had%20just%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-ai-capex-infrastructure-data-center-wars-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremove%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20list%20of%20permitted%20uses%20in%20a%20plan%20to%20redevelop%20several%20parcels%20of%20land.%20While%20no%20data%20center%20had%20yet%20been%20proposed%2C%20even%20the%20possibility%20that%20a%20data%20center%20could%20someday%20end%20up%20there%20raised%20alarm%20among%20city%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20city%20administration%20is%20asking%20the%20council%20to%20amend%20the%20redevelopment%20plan%20to%20remove%20data%20centers%20as%20a%20permitted%20use%2C%20and%20to%20reinsert%20the%20requirement%20for%20inclusion%20of%20a%20park%20on%20the%20site%20that's%20provided%20in%20the%20prior%20redevelopment%2C%26quot%3B%20New%20Brunswick's%20city%20planner%20Daniel%20Dominguez%20said%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarge%2C%20warehouse-style%20data%20centers%20have%20become%20a%20flash%20point%20for%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommunities%20across%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Big%20Tech%20and%20other%20AI%20companies%20look%20to%20power%20the%20large%20language%20models%20and%20chatbots%20they%20say%20are%20going%20to%20change%20the%20world.%20Those%20data%20centers%2C%20however%2C%20can%20be%20a%20drain%20on%20water%20resources%20and%20power%20grids%2C%20increase%20pollution%2C%20and%20decrease%20the%20quality%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-development-true-cost-environmental-impact-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvestigation%20by%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20last%20year%20found%20that%20over%201%2C200%20data%20centers%20had%20been%20approved%20for%20construction%20across%20the%20US%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%20These%20data%20centers%2C%20the%20report%20found%2C%20could%20consume%20as%20much%20power%20as%20entire%20US%20states%20and%20guzzle%20enormous%20amounts%20of%20water%20daily%20in%20drought-stricken%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20Brunswick%2C%20those%20environmental%20concerns%20were%20top%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommunity%20members%20cited%20concerns%20over%20environmental%20impact%2C%20energy%20consumption%2C%20water%20usage%2C%20noise%20pollution%2C%20and%20the%20broader%20implications%20of%20allowing%20large%E2%80%90scale%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20data%20infrastructure%20to%20expand%20into%20residential%20and%20public%20community%20spaces%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Climate%20Revolution%20Action%20Network%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20local%20environmental%20activist%20group%20that%20helped%20organize%20opposition%20to%20the%20redevelopment%20plan%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20residents%20and%20environmental%20advocates%20attended%20a%20New%20Brunswick%20City%20Council%20meeting%20to%20discuss%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20Dominguez%20said%20the%20inclusion%20of%20a%20potential%20data%20center%20in%20the%20redevelopment%20plan%20was%20intended%20to%20%26quot%3Bdiversify%20the%20commercial%20development%20site%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20critical%20to%20the%20project.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttendees%20cheered%20after%20the%20city%20council%20ultimately%20voted%20to%20nix%20the%20data%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20like%20to%20thank%20the%20council%20for%20deciding%20to%20scrap%20what%20many%20people%20did%20not%20want%20in%20their%20neighborhoods%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20attendee%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20these%20kinds%20of%20centers%20in%20here%20that%20are%20going%20to%20take%20resources%20from%20the%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20Brunswick%20is%20one%20among%20many%20communities%20across%20the%20country%20fighting%20potential%20data%20center%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3