%20will%20be%2C%20effective%20immediately%2C%20raising%20the%2010%25%20Worldwide%20Tariff%20on%20Countries%2C%20many%20of%20which%20have%20been%20'ripping'%20the%20U.S.%20off%20for%20decades%2C%20without%20retribution%20(until%20I%20came%20along!)%2C%20to%20the%20fully%20allowed%2C%20and%20legally%20tested%2C%2015%25%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%206-3%20decision%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20Trump%20did%20not%20have%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-reaction-supreme-court-scotus-tariff-ruling-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eauthority%20to%20impose%20his%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20International%20Emergency%20Economic%20Powers%20Act%2C%20a%20national%20security%20law%20that%20allows%20the%20president%20to%20regulate%20economic%20activity%20during%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%20following%20the%20decision%2C%20Trump%20said%20he%20would%20use%20a%20separate%20authority%20to%20impose%20a%2010%25%20global%20tariff%20on%20top%20of%20any%20existing%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20separate%20authority%20is%20known%20as%20Section%20122%2C%20which%20can%20only%20be%20imposed%20for%20150%20days.%20After%20that%2C%20Congress%20must%20vote%20to%20extend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20official%20later%20said%20that%20countries%20being%20tariffed%20under%20the%20authority%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20struck%20down%20will%20now%20be%20subject%20to%20that%2010%25%20tariff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20IEEPA%20no%20longer%20applicable%2C%20those%20countries%20will%20now%20be%20tariffed%20at%20the%20global%2010%25%20tariff%20using%20the%20Section%20122%20legal%20authority%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%2C%20however%2C%20only%20temporary%20as%20the%20Administration%20will%20be%20pursuing%20other%20legal%20authorities%20to%20implement%20more%20appropriate%20or%20pre-negotiated%20tariff%20rates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president's%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Saturday%2C%20while%20short%20on%20details%2C%20indicated%20he%20would%20raise%20that%20tariff%20to%2015%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IEEPA-justified%20tariffs%20have%20been%20among%20Trump's%20most%20powerful%20weapons%20in%20his%20efforts%20to%20renegotiate%20trade%20agreements%20worldwide.%20They%20included%20Trump's%20so-called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-liberation-day-reciprocal-tariffs-speech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20announced%20in%20April%2C%20which%20are%20at%20least%2010%25%20on%20nearly%20every%20country%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20next%20short%20number%20of%20months%2C%20the%20Trump%20Administration%20will%20determine%20and%20issue%20the%20new%20and%20legally%20permissible%20Tariffs%2C%20which%20will%20continue%20our%20extraordinarily%20successful%20process%20of%20Making%20America%20Great%20Again%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20president%20wrote%20in%20his%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-raise-global-tariff-supreme-court-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771693351000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6999e518156648bc16a8a821%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-raise-global-tariff-supreme-court-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20not%20giving%20up%20on%20his%20tariff%20strategy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pgelling%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Gelling)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A505%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-raise-global-tariff-supreme-court-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22