0been%20supportive%20of%20him%20in%20his%20quest%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20US%20Ski%20Team%20and%20the%202034%20Olympics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDTwXzhfjNk4%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESarah%20Canzano%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgavincanz_8%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGavin%20Canzano%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20the%20mom%20of%20an%20elite%20teenage%20athlete.%20My%20husband%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdownhill-skiing-insane-photos-winter-olympics-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edownhill%20skier%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20and%20he%20taught%20our%20boys%2C%20Gavin%20and%20Deacon%2C%20to%20ski%20when%20they%20were%20about%20two%20or%20three.%20I%20don't%20ski%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGavin%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-a-shy-person-to-open-up-quickly-2016-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshy%20and%20reserved%20kid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20he%20was%20a%20different%20kid%20on%20the%20mountain.%20He%20was%20so%20confident.%20We%20used%20to%20say%20that%20skiing%20was%20like%20oxygen%20to%20him.%20It's%20where%20he%20is%20at%20his%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e169712c-645c-4705-b4dd-7ea12b253b81%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20was%20easy%20to%20recognize%20his%20talent%20early%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGavin%20began%20skiing%20with%20the%20Bristol%20Mountain%20Freestyle%20team%20when%20he%20was%20around%208%20years%20old.%20It's%20a%20feeder%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-us-ski-team-why-women-tear-the-acls-more-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20Ski%20Team%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20apparent%20quickly%20that%20he%20was%20very%20good%20in%20the%20air.%20In%202024%2C%20when%20he%20was%2014%2C%20he%20was%20invited%20to%20Lake%20Placid%2C%20N.Y.%2C%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20US%20Ski%20Team's%20Project%20Gold%2C%20an%20aerial%20camp.%20He%20was%20all%20in%20on%20aerial%20skiing%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22427%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Skier%20posing%20for%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698b57caa645d11881890cc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22320%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESarah%20Canzano's%20son%20started%20doing%20aerial%20ski%20when%20he%20was%208%20years%20old.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sarah%20Canzano%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2015%2C%20he%20is%20part%20of%20the%20US%20Ski%20Team's%20national%20development%20program%20for%20aerials.%20He%20trains%20with%20his%20national%20teammates%20at%20the%20Olympic%20Training%20Center%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-ski-resorts-in-northeast-us-east-coast-skiing-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELake%20Placid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20travels%20for%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e164339-90bf-49a4-9ef9-2bd5c0172c49%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20can%20be%20challenging%20to%20raise%20a%20teenage%20athlete%20and%20create%20balance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20a%2015-year-old%20boy.%20He%20makes%20mistakes.%20But%20as%20long%20as%20he's%20working%20hard%2C%20and%20doing%20the%20best%20he%20can%20at%20school%20and%20being%20a%20good%20human%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20make%20sacrifices%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20also%20had%20conversations%20with%20Gavin%20about%20the%20sacrifices%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20make%20on%20this%20path.%20That%20means%20school%20is%20going%20to%20be%20harder%2C%20because%20he's%20going%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-mom-lets-her-kid-skip-school-every-month-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emiss%20a%20lot%20of%20school%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20see%20his%20school%20friends%20that%20much%20when%20he's%20competing%20and%20traveling.%20But%2C%20we've%20always%20told%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20work%20hard%20for%20you%20as%20long%20as%20you%20are%20working%20hard%20for%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226224%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20posing%20for%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698b5841a645d11881890cd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224149%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESarah%20Canzano's%20family%20has%20had%20to%20adjust%20to%20her%20oldest's%20ski%20training.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sarah%20Canzano%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20loves%20what%20he%20does%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20support%20him.%20If%20he%20ever%20got%20to%20the%20point%20where%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20do%20it%20anymore%2C%20we%20would%20never%20make%20him.%20It%20sounds%20insane%20considering%20the%20investment%20we've%20made%2C%20but%20it's%20his%20body%2C%20his%20life.%20We%20are%20also%20teaching%20him%20to%20advocate%20for%20himself%20because%20we%20won't%20always%20be%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22718d1b2c-c54e-45ff-a1a8-1639f5074dba%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe've%20had%20to%20change%20our%20lifestyle%20to%20accommodate%20him%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-time-using-travel-advisor-group-trip-paris-worth-it-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20we%20like%20to%20travel%20as%20a%20family.%20Before%2C%20we'd%20be%20off%20to%20an%20island%20somewhere%20every%20break%2C%20but%20now%20I'm%20spending%20that%20time%20standing%20on%20a%20mountain.%20We've%20definitely%20had%20to%20change%20our%20plans%20several%20times%20for%20him%2C%20but%20we%20never%20put%20that%20burden%20on%20him.%20This%20is%20our%20family's%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20divide%20and%20conquer%20a%20lot.%20A%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20just%20my%20husband%20or%20just%20me%20will%20travel%20with%20Gavin%2C%20so%20that%20Deacon%20can%20be%20home%2C%20in%20school%2C%20and%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20pursuing%20his%20hobbies.%20Pat%20and%20I%20are%20apart%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20we%20also%20try%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20that%20one-on-one%20time%20with%20our%20kids%2C%20and%20the%20moments%20we%20have%20together%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeacon%20is%20the%20real%20hero%20here%3B%20he%20is%20such%20a%20supportive%20little%20brother.%20He%20goes%20along%20for%20the%20ride%20with%20minimal%20complaints%20and%20is%20Gavin's%20biggest%20fan.%20He's%20so%20proud%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287958b47-a97a-4b22-9df9-98a9bbe8ee63%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe're%20taking%20it%20one%20step%20at%20a%20time%2C%20but%20the%20Olympics%20are%20the%20goal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20want%20him%20to%20have%20fun.%20He%20had%20me%20write%20%26quot%3Bhave%20fun%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20skis%2C%20so%20if%20he's%20having%20a%20bad%20day%20or%20a%20couple%20of%20bad%20jumps%2C%20he%20can%20remind%20himself%20that%20this%20is%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gavin%20Cazano%20after%20competing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698b5afbe1ba468a96abc411%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22427%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESarah%20Canzano's%20son%20is%20training%20to%20compete%20in%20the%202034%20Olympics.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sarah%20Canzano%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20also%20serious.%20We%20might%20consider%20looking%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-companies-sponsor-h1b-visas-jpmorga