ent%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20woman%20on%20the%20left%2C%20and%20the%20front%20of%20a%20home%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6966bf7004eda4732f2f0447%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWendy%20Martin%20is%20bowing%20out%20of%20the%20Airbnb%20game.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Wendy%20Martin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAirbnb%20host%20Wendy%20Martin%20delisted%20her%20Ohio%20property%20after%20more%20than%20two%20years%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bad%20experiences%20with%20guests%20were%20no%20longer%20worth%20the%20headache%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20plans%20to%20rent%20to%20her%20daughter%20instead%2C%20which%20will%20make%20her%20less%20money%20but%20give%20her%20peace%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Wendy%20Martin%2C%2050%2C%20who%20chose%20to%20delist%20the%20Airbnb%20on%20her%20property%20near%20Dayton%2C%20Ohio%2C%20after%20bad%20experiences%20with%20guests.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20purchased%20our%20property%20from%20a%20family%20member%20who%20was%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-bought-airbnb-made-60000-three-years-2015-07%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edoing%20Airbnb%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20owners%20enjoyed%20it%20and%20were%20pretty%20successful%20at%20it.%20They%20made%20us%20quite%20a%20deal%20on%20the%20property%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20just%20keep%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcafe-owners-buy-building-make-100000-renting-on-airbnb-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eas%20an%20Airbnb%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20small%20single-family%20home.%20It%20was%20built%20in%201910%20as%20the%20original%20home%20on%20the%20property%20while%20the%20family%20was%20having%20the%20main%20house%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20really%20close%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-two-car-garage-massachusetts-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eback%20of%20the%20main%20house%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20I%20were%20in%20my%20home%20office%20and%20there%20were%20people%20in%20the%20living%20room%20of%20the%20Airbnb%2C%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20you%20what%20they%20looked%20like%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20little%20bit%20awkward%20to%20be%20like%20a%20traditional%20rental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20thought%20Airbnb%2C%20with%20people%20who%20were%20here%20short-term%20coming%20and%20going%2C%20would%20be%20a%20really%20great%20way%20to%20give%20us%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20extra%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20three%20bedrooms%2C%20one-and-a-half%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20probably%20about%201%2C300%20square%20feet.%20It%20has%20a%20full%20kitchen%2C%20washer%2C%20and%20dryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20located%20on%20our%20six-acre%20property%2C%20so%20people%20have%20full%20use%20of%20the%20trails%20and%20the%20woods%2C%20and%20we've%20got%20a%20little%20stream%2C%20and%20they%20can%20feed%20the%20fish%20in%20the%20koi%20pond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20koi%20pond.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6966bfd704eda4732f2f0456%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20koi%20pond%20on%20the%20property.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Wendy%20Martin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20within%2020%20minutes%20of%20four%20or%20five%20different%20colleges.%20We're%2015%20minutes%20to%20Wright-Patterson%20Air%20Force%20Base.%20We're%20an%20hour%20to%20Columbus%2C%20Ohio%2C%20and%20an%20hour%20to%20Cincinnati%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20location%20is%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20get%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20vacation%20rentals%2C%20but%20we%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20coming%20to%20visit%20family%20or%20military%20PCSes%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20college%20graduations%20and%20new%20student%20drop-offs%20and%20parent%20weekends%20%E2%80%94%20things%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20about%20March%20until%20the%20end%20of%20December%20every%20year%2C%20we've%20had%20almost%20no%20weekends%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20owners%20had%20great%20success%20with%20it%2C%20and%20they%20met%20some%20great%20people%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20that%20we%20would%20continue%20doing%20that.%20We%20eventually%20re-listed%20it%20as%20our%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbought-home-with-friend-coinvesting-real-estate-pros-cons-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eafter%20we%20bought%20the%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20been%20running%20it%20ever%20since.%20We've%20been%20hosting%20for%20about%20two-and-a-half%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214eb451e-db1d-44c5-95be-b45002f88b9a%5C%22%3EBad%20experiences%20with%20guests%20made%20us%20leave%20the%20platform%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-with-20-airbnbs-quitting-for-more-direct-bookings-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etaking%20the%20property%20off%20Airbnb%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20few%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrimarily%2C%20I%20was%20recently%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20mild%20form%20of%20leukemia.%20It's%20not%20nearly%20as%20scary%20for%20me%20as%20it%20is%20for%20some%20people%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20know%20when%20I%20might%20get%20sick%2C%20and%20at%20some%20point%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20too%20sick%20to%20actually%20run%20the%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20two-and-a-half%20years%2C%20we've%20had%20three%20really%20terrible%20experiences%20%E2%80%94%20and%20two%20of%20those%20were%20the%20same%20guests.%20This%20was%20probably%20the%20first%20time%20that%20it%20was%20frustrating%20for%20me%20to%20be%20a%20host.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20we%20had%20guests%20stay%20here%20for%20five%20days%2C%20and%20the%20two%20guys%20just%20hung%20out.%20They%20brought%20a%20couple%20of%20big%2C%20stinky%20dogs%2C%20because%20we%20allow%20pets%20with%20no%20pet%20fee%2C%20and%20they%20were%20basically%20just%20slobs.%20For%20some%20reason%2C%20they%20drove%20up%20the%20driveway%20all%20the%20way%20up%20into%20the%20yard%20on%20the%20grass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20yard%20on%20an%20Airbnb%20property.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6966c00404eda4732f2f045e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMartin's%20yard.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Wendy%20Martin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20didn't%20break%20anything%20or%20trash%20the%20house%2C%20but%20the%20house%20was%20pretty%20gross%20after%20they%20got%20out%20of%20there%2C%20so%20it%20took%20us%20a%20while%20to%20clean.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20I%20didn't%20realize%20the%20same%20guest%20who%20had%20booked%20before%20was%20booking%20the%20house%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20before%20he%20showed%20up%2C%20I%20realized%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%20this%20guy%20again%3F%26quot%3B%20So%20that%20was%20frustrating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20time%2C%20a%20guy%20said%20he%20and%20his%20friends%20were%20coming%20to%20stay.%20They%20stayed%20for%20like%2010%20days%2C%20and%20they%20trashed%20our%20house.%20I%20mean%2C%20just%20filth.%20Food%20wrappers%20stuffed%20under%20mattresses%20and%20behind%20beds.%20They%20had%20dumped%20a%20pot%20of%20cooked%20food%20in%20the%20flower%20bed%20in%20the%20front%20yard.%20They%20melted%20a%20remote%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20extra%20cleaning%20and%20the%20damage%20that%20they%20did%2C%20I%20filed%20a%20reimbursement%20request%20with%20Airbnb%20for%20%24160.%20I%20sent%20all%20the%20documentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6966c033764ca5f34d2a639e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20room.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Wendy%20Martin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20asking%20for%20an%20exorbitant%20amount.%20And%20then%20they%20just%20paid%20me%20%2410%20total%20for%20a%20remote%20control.%20I%20would've%20rather%20they%20sent%20me%20%240.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%5B%3Cem%3EEd%20note%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20When%20reached%20for%20comment%20about%20Martin's%20complaint%2C%20Airbnb%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20thoroughly%20reviewed%20the%20photos%20submitted%2C%20as%20we%20do%20with%20all%20host%20damage%20claims%2C%20and%20partly%20reimbursed%20the%20host%20for%20the%20damage%20found.%20We%20value%20our%20hosts%20and%20do%20our%20best%20to%20support%20them%20throughout%20their%20hosting%20journey.%26quot%3B%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20made%20the%20decision%20that%20maybe%20this%20isn't%20going%20to%20be%20for%20us.%20My%20daughter%20and%20her%20girlfriend%20and%20their%20best%20friend%20live%20nice%20and%20close.%20They're%20in%20their%20mid-20s%2C%20living%20in%20college%20apartments%2C%20so%20we%20agreed%20to%20let%20the%20girls%20come%20rent%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'll%20make%20about%20half%20the%20money%20we%20would%20normally%20make%2C%20but%20I%20now%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20be%20a%20cleaner.%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20replace%20all%20the%20snacks%20and%20water.%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20replacing%20linens%20or%20towels%20or%20providing%20shampoo%20or%20any%20of%20that%20other%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cefba8f3-be26-4761-90d7-edab2f3cce3e%5C%22%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20rent%20to%20my%20daughter%20instead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20use%20smart%20pricing%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20charged%20%24125%20a%20night%20and%20a%20%2475%20cleaning%20fee.%20If%20people%20stay%20for%20more%20than%20seven%20days%20or%20more%20than%2015%20days%2C%20then%20I'd%20give%20them%20a%2010%25%20or%20a%2015%25%20discount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20weekend%20stay%2C%20we're%20usually%20clearing%20about%20%24325%20for%20a%20two-night%20stay%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20could%20be%20one%20person%2C%20or%20it%20could%20be%20six%20people%20because%20we%20allow%20up%20to%20six%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20charge%20extra%20for%20anybody.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20not%20a%20tourist%20town%2C%20so%20for%20the%20people%20we're%20serving%2C%20we're%20fulfilling%20some%20kind%20of%20need%20for%20them.%20People%20do%20not%20come%20to%20Dayton%2C%20Ohio%2C%20to%20hang%20out%20and%20live%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20typically%2C%20the%20people%20that%20are%20coming%20here%20are%20the%20same%20people%20that%20we%20would%20have%20coming%20if%20it%20were%20our%20family%2C%20and%20it%20was%20important%20to%20me%20that%20we%20provided%20someplace%20nice%20that%20people%20could%20also%20afford%2C%20without%20it%20being%20so%20cheap%20that%20we%20were%20getting%20guests%20who%20just%20showed%20up%20and%20trashed%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6966c04e64858d02d2184b81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Wendy%20Martin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20hosted%20people%20who%20have%20unfortunately%20lost%20family%20members%20in%20tragic%20accidents%2C%20or%20we%20had%20one%20repeat%20guest%20who%20came%20because%20her%20dad%20was%20in%20assisted%20living%2C%20so%20she%20would%20come%20for%20the%20same%20long%20weekend%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20every%20month%20for%20nine%20months%2C%20and%20she%20stayed%20with%20us%20every%20week%20or%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20six%20bookings%20going%20into%20the%20new%20year%20already%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20in%20March%20and%20April%20%E2%80%94%20so%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20each%20of%20them%2C%20explaining%20that%20I%20had%20to%20cancel%20their%20stays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20met%20some%20really%20cool%20people%20who%20have%20stayed%20with%20us%20multiple%20times%2C%20and%20it%20kind%20of%20sucks%20to%20take%20that%20option%20away%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20a%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6966c077764ca5f34d2a63ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22795%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20front%20of%20the%20Airbnb%20property%20on%20Martin's%20property.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Wendy%20Martin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENormally%2C%20we%20bring%20in%20about%20%242%2C300%20a%20month%20on%20average.%20But%20we're%20going%20to%20charge%20my%20daughter%20and%20her%20roommates%20about%20%241%2C300%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20includes%20all%20utilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they're%20also%20going%20to%20be%20doing%20some%20yard%20work%2C%20which%20will%20save%20us%20some%20additional%20money.%20So%20I%20think%20it'll%20all%20end%20up%20coming%20out%20in%20the%20wash%20because%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20provide%20linens%20and%20snacks%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20pay%20somebody%20to%20come%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I'm%20healthy%20again%20and%20they%20decide%20to%20move%20on%2C%20then%20likely%20we%20will%20go%20to%20something%20like%20Furnish%20Finder%20and%20do%20something%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaving-airbnb-for-long-term-rental-arizona-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20little%20more%20long-term%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20I%20can%20have%20a%20little%20more%20control%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAxel%20Springer%2C%20Insider%20Inc.'s%20parent%20company%2C%20is%20an%20investor%20in%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-airbnb-delisted-home-hosting-bad-guests-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771678021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6966bfa1764ca5f34d2a637e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-airbnb-delisted-home-hosting-bad-guests-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wendy%20Martin's%20Airbnb%20property%20in%20Dayton%2C%20Ohio%2C%20made%20her%20money%20and%20she%20enjoyed%20hosting%20%E2%80%94%20until%20three%20bad%20experiences%20with%20guests%20made%20her%20quit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-airbnb-delisted-home-hosting-bad-guests-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Walmart%20and%20Google%20became%20key%20to%20the%20search%20for%20Nancy%20Guthrie%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walmart%20store%3B%20Google%20building.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69976cd2e1ba468a96ac56ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalmart%20and%20Google%20have%20been%20assisting%20law%20enforcement%20in%20the%20disappearance%20of%20Nancy%20Guthrie.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Bell%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Jeremy%20Moeller%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20and%20Walmart%20have%20been%20assisting%20authorities%20in%20the%20disappearance%20of%20Nancy%20Guthrie.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestigators%20recovered%20footage%20from%20the%20woman's%20Nest%20doorbell%20camera%20with%20Google's%20help.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWalmart%20is%20tracking%20backpack%20purchases%20linked%20to%20the%20ca