.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20in%20that%20moment%20of%20loss%20and%20abandonment%2C%20Rupam%20found%20the%20spark%20of%20a%20promise%20%E2%80%94%20to%20her%20mother%2C%20and%20to%20herself%3A%20%3Cem%3EI%20will%20do%20something%20big%20in%20life.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20at%20just%2022%2C%20she%20has%20kept%20that%20promise%20by%20clearing%20the%20Jharkhand%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(JPSC)%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20in%20her%20first%20attempt%2C%20without%20coaching%2C%20without%20guidance%2C%20and%20against%20all%20odds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20long%20road%20to%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20losing%20their%20parents%2C%20Rupam%20and%20her%20sister%20resolved%20to%20fight%20back%20instead%20of%20succumbing%20to%20despair.%20Finances%20were%20tight%2C%20and%20emotional%20support%20was%20absent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-1-1757075398.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20losing%20both%20parents%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20Rupam%20Sonali%20vowed%20to%20fulfill%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20dream.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-1-1757075398.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-1-1757075398-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-