ttps%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%2012%20years%20later%2C%20she%20smiles%20when%20she%20recalls%20that%20moment.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20stayed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20never%20have%20learnt%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296463%2Fjharkhand-teacher-sapan-patralekh-teaches-parents-and-grandparents-improves-literacy-rate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrue%20meaning%20of%20teaching%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWearing%20many%20hats%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%20now%20teaches%20Sanskrit%2C%20English%2C%20and%20Hindi%20at%20an%20upper%20primary%20school%20in%20D%20Block%2C%20Raebareli.%20The%20school%20has%20only%20three%20teachers%20in%20total%2C%20each%20one%20covering%20multiple%20subjects.%20Between%20them%2C%20they%20handle%20everything%20from%20mathematics%20to%20science%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20it%20is%20their%20area%20of%20expertise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20rural%20schools%2C%20you%20are%20not%20just%20a%20subject%20teacher%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sangeeta%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20a%20counsellor%2C%20a%20friend%2C%20sometimes%20even%20a%20nurse%20or%20a%20mother%20figure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-1-1757060631.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Her%20efforts%20resulted%20in%20a%20steep%20rise%20in%20regular%20attendance%2C%20from%20fewer%20than%2030%20to%20100%20students%20within%20a%20month%20of%20her%20intensive%20community%20engagement.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F